{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9fe14342ab","title":"对周敦祥来信的批语和复信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b7a9dad989","index":0,"year":1955,"month":2,"day":3,"articleId":"9fe14342ab"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"eb7825b2f5","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"9fe14342ab","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周敦祥，五四时期曾加入毛泽东领导的新民学会，1955年4月后被安排为湖南省文史研究馆馆员。"},{"id":"3de2105136","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"9fe14342ab","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指周教祥1955年1月10日给毛泽东的信。信中说，1921年她曾和张国基一起到南洋办教育，1935年回国。新中国成立后因找不到正式工作，曾想到华北革命大学学习，后因华北革命大学从第四期停办，学习未成，工作不得，经济困难，个人生活也无法维持，希望毛泽东能给她介绍一个工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"638df6cb26","type":"title","text":"对周敦祥\"来信的批语和复信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"9fe14342ab"},{"id":"eb7825b2f5","type":"paragraph","text":"将此信转寄湖南省委统战部，看是否能在省参事室及文史【馆]给以位置。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"9fe14342ab"},{"id":"3de2105136","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"9fe14342ab"},{"id":"d19decb64a","type":"paragraph","text":"二月三日教祥先生：","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"9fe14342ab"},{"id":"392ffa7e4d","type":"paragraph","text":"来信收到。尊况甚表同情。已请湖南省委统一战线部的量设法毛泽东全集第三十四卷为助，未知能如愿否，你可就近接治。如有急切困难，尚望见告。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"9fe14342ab"},{"id":"579bf69a6b","type":"paragraph","text":"顺祝进步","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"9fe14342ab"},{"id":"ca8ac1a930","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","article